    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it has been such a joy to own! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes and weekend getaways. While it\u2019s seen some love and has a bit of character, it still runs like a charm and looks great on the road. This is the perfect chance to grab a dependable car that\u2019s ready for many more miles of fun. I'd love for it to go to a good home, so come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
