    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-focused example featuring a high-revving naturally aspirated flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. This unit boasts a limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction and an active suspension management system that maintains composure through high-lateral G maneuvers. The mid-engine architecture provides an exceptional polar moment of inertia, while the upgraded four-piston monobloc calipers ensure consistent thermal management under load. Mechanically sound with a linear power band and visceral exhaust note, this chassis represents a pure analog experience. Recent service includes a full cooling system flush and a fresh set of high-performance summer compounds.",
