      "description": "Presenting a well-maintained example that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its honest road history. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery remains supple, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster consistent with its mileage. Every electronic feature, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine pulls strongly and the transmission shifts with precision, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil service and a brake pad replacement. This is a dependable, turn-key vehicle ready for its next owner who appreciates a car that has been cared for with pride.",
